title: Who’d win, Darth Maul (TCW Season 7) or Justin Bieber (Yummy Era)? - Quora

response.answer_text: I’m pretty convinced there’s not a living thing on our planet that can defeat Maul. That includes Justin Bieber. One of these people has killed several jedi, created a crime syndicate, and has a double bladed laser sword. The other is a physically average human, who’s claim to fame is singing songs for pre teen girls. Let’s do some quick math. The only chance Bieber has is Disney threatening to sue Maul for attempted murder of one of their talents.

Are we putting a trained Sith against a boy artist. Even strapped and with his bodyguards Darth Maul, will slice him in half. Who knows tho maybe he’s a fan and won’t….. Ask Disney aren’t they in charge of this…
